title: Polly Scattergood - Polly Scattergood (2009) [VIPER666]
description:
Polly Scattergood is a singer songwriter from Essex, England. She has been described as ethereal, dark, intense and quirky. Album was released March 9, 2009 in the United Kingdom. The album will be released in the United States on 19 May.
